(34, 1, '2018-12-28 13:39:14', '2018-12-28 13:39:14', '<p class=\"about-me-paragraph\"><strong>I\'m <a href=\"http://localhost/wordpress/about\">Gurinder Singh</a> I live in Belgium, currently I\'m pursuing a Bachelor\'s degree in Computer Science</strong>, specializing as a Software &amp; Systems Engineer. I\'ve got great amount of passion for developing stuff that ease our day to day life. Aside from coding, I really enjoy travelling, politics, entertainment (movies, series...) and doing sports.</p>\r\n<p class=\"about-me-paragraph\">If you\'d like to know more about me as a person or the projects I\'ve done so far, visit  my <a href=\"http://localhost/wordpress/projects\">projects</a> or <a href=\"http://localhost/wordpress/about\">about </a>page. If you\'re interested in <a href=\"http://localhost/wordpress/contact\">contacting me</a>, be sure to do so!</p>\r\n\r\n', 'Hey there!', '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'hey-there', '', '', '2018-12-29 17:09:48', '2018-12-29 17:09:48', '', 0, 'http://localhost/wordpress/?p=34', 0, 'post', '', 0),
